way into my family.

57:49.596 --> 57:52.773
You chose this role, and now
you're gonna fucking play it.

58:01.695 --> 58:06.004
So you can be Esther for
now and live a life that anyone

58:06.047 --> 58:08.354
would kill to have.

58:08.397 --> 58:10.487
