and get shipped back to Estonia

58:10.530 --> 58:12.967
in handcuffs.

58:13.011 --> 58:14.491
What do you say?

58:29.157 --> 58:30.158
I'm sorry I scared you.

58:30.202 --> 58:30.724
I'm sorry.

58:31.246 --> 58:32.421
I'm sorry.

58:32.465 --> 58:34.162
We should've never
left you alone.

58:35.599 --> 58:36.556
What happened?

58:36.600 --> 58:37.862
She fell off her bike.

58:37.905 --> 58:39.603
