Yeah.

58:51.615 --> 58:52.964
So what does this mean?

58:53.007 --> 58:55.227
Oh, it means.. She's not a kid.

58:55.270 --> 58:58.839
She is a grown woman and we
cannot underestimate her.

58:58.883 --> 59:00.798
