mother, she's a psychopath

59:00.841 --> 59:02.582
living in our fucking house.

59:03.061 --> 59:05.150
Shh.

59:05.803 --> 59:07.544
So we just have to
live with this person?

59:07.587 --> 59:09.241
I didn't say that.

59:09.284 --> 59:15.073
So then can we just, you know,
make it look like an accident?

59:15.726 --> 59:17.118
It's too soon.

59:17.162 --> 59:18.946
We need to think about this.

59:19.381 --> 59:20.426
So she just owns us now?

59:20.469 --> 59:21.340
No, no.

59:21.383 --> 59:23.734
