Dr. Segar is today.

1:00:35.893 --> 1:00:38.504
A problem we wouldn't have if
you hadn't talked to the parrot.

1:00:38.547 --> 1:00:39.679
Sydney was a macaw.

1:00:39.723 --> 1:00:41.333
A what?

1:00:41.376 --> 1:00:42.813
All macaw's are parrots.

1:00:42.856 --> 1:00:45.380
But not all fucking
parrots are macaws.

1:00:48.775 --> 1:00:50.385
What are we gonna
do about that?

1:00:52.257 --> 1:00:54.346
Oh, we make her believe.

1:00:54.389 --> 1:00:55.869
Together.

1:00:57.218 --> 1:00:59.090
One of our goals here is
helping Esther acclimate back

1:00:59.133 --> 1:01:01.309
into life within
the family unit.

1:01:01.353 --> 1:01:03.921
Part of that is remembering
your shared history.

1:01:03.964 --> 1:01:07.141
Moments you had, the fun
things you did together before.

1:01:07.185 --> 1:01:09.578
