that means a lot to you

1:01:09.622 --> 1:01:11.276
and to Esther?

1:01:11.319 --> 1:01:12.625
Oh, God, there are so many.

1:01:12.669 --> 1:01:14.758
Huh?

1:01:16.150 --> 1:01:18.544
Um, there was
Christmas in Paris.

1:01:18.587 --> 1:01:19.806
The summer in Tuscany.

1:01:19.850 --> 1:01:20.764
Yellowstone?

1:01:20.807 --> 1:01:22.156
Yeah, that's up there.

1:01:22.200 --> 1:01:24.202
I was six.

1:01:24.245 --> 1:01:28.119
We saw bears.. And a, a
