leaned down to eat grass,

1:01:43.221 --> 1:01:45.614
daddy fell right over his
head onto the ground.

1:01:45.658 --> 1:01:47.660
He had dirt all
over his face.

1:01:47.704 --> 1:01:49.706
It was even in his teeth!

1:01:49.749 --> 1:01:50.968
I can't believe you're
telling this story.

1:01:51.011 --> 1:01:52.665
