1:06:26.286 --> 1:06:28.201
Honey, hey, what's wrong?

1:06:28.245 --> 1:06:29.420
Dad, she's fine.

1:06:29.463 --> 1:06:30.551
Just give her some space.

1:06:30.595 --> 1:06:31.248
She's fine.

1:06:31.291 --> 1:06:32.727
Yeah.

1:06:32.771 --> 1:06:34.164
She's probably tired from
all that piano playing.

1:07:04.759 --> 1:07:06.718
[knocking]

1:07:08.111 --> 1:07:09.155
Can I come in?

1:07:09.199 --> 1:07:10.678
Mm-hmm.

1:07:10.722 --> 1:07:11.723
Are you okay?

1:07:11.766 --> 1:07:13.203
What happened down there?

1:07:14.160 --> 1:07:18.295
I, uh, I don't really
