my favorite time to paint.

1:07:27.347 --> 1:07:28.783
Do you, you wanna come join me?

1:07:28.827 --> 1:07:30.611
Yes, I would love to.

1:07:30.655 --> 1:07:32.265
I'll see you downstairs.

1:07:34.137 --> 1:07:38.837
♪ soothing music

1:08:07.387 --> 1:08:08.954
This is a
such a great space.

1:08:08.997 --> 1:08:10.956
I'm glad you like it.

1:08:10.999 --> 1:08:15.003
Every artist needs a space to
