even know to look.

1:08:24.187 --> 1:08:25.492
I really like that.

1:08:39.027 --> 1:08:40.290
So much paint.

1:08:40.333 --> 1:08:41.856
Yeah, I'm a messy painter.

1:08:41.900 --> 1:08:43.554
Allen: Drives your mother crazy.

1:08:48.341 --> 1:08:50.213
I think I'm, I think
I'm done for the night.

1:08:50.256 --> 1:08:51.518
Just turn the lights off.

1:08:51.562 --> 1:08:54.260
Have a good night.

