1:09:41.220 --> 1:09:42.787
most men are.

1:09:44.267 --> 1:09:47.879
Well, if you'll excuse me,
I'm gonna go upstairs

1:09:47.922 --> 1:09:50.098
and fuck my husband.

1:09:55.756 --> 1:09:57.758
He really is a new
man since you came back.

1:09:58.933 --> 1:09:59.847
Thanks for that.

1:10:02.285 --> 1:10:06.202
♪ tense music

1:10:36.797 --> 1:10:39.060
Hey, you.

1:10:51.812 --> 1:10:55.294
