1:11:36.509 --> 1:11:38.511
and you get back out there.

1:11:38.555 --> 1:11:40.426
Yeah, okay.

1:11:40.470 --> 1:11:41.471
We're not hurting, are we?

1:11:41.514 --> 1:11:42.167
No, no.

1:11:42.210 --> 1:11:43.908
Not at all.

1:11:43.951 --> 1:11:46.954
I.. You are a great painter.

1:11:46.998 --> 1:11:47.955
People miss seeing your work.

1:11:50.654 --> 1:11:52.308
Thank you.

1:11:54.092 --> 1:11:55.702
Is that bacon?

1:11:58.096 --> 1:12:00.272
Oh, it's heaven!

1:12:03.710 --> 1:12:05.146
Good morning, daddy.

1:12:05.190 --> 1:12:06.060
Crepe?

1:12:06.104 --> 1:12:07.192
Yes, please.

1:12:07.235 --> 1:12:08.976
Allen: Is there anything
you can't do?

1:12:09.020 --> 1:12:10.108
Mummy?

1:12:10.151 --> 1:12:11.152
Tricia: Oh, no, thanks.

1:12:11.196 --> 1:12:13.198
I'm gonna make my
