1:12:20.814 --> 1:12:22.686
Just the way you like it.

1:12:23.251 --> 1:12:24.992
Try it.

1:12:25.036 --> 1:12:27.386
I'm-I'm not really that hungry.

1:12:27.430 --> 1:12:28.822
I'll-I'll have it.

