1:13:19.133 --> 1:13:20.396
I wanted to show you
something, though.

1:13:20.439 --> 1:13:21.397
Here.

1:13:24.965 --> 1:13:26.837
It's the one in the center.

1:13:30.144 --> 1:13:32.233
Dean at Woodley
is a friend of mine.

1:13:32.277 --> 1:13:34.322
Woodley is the best art
school in the country.

1:13:34.366 --> 1:13:35.193
You're scary good, Esther.

1:13:35.236 --> 1:13:36.542
